description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 55, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 275, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 5 for East, Leverage for South, and Stringalong for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10555-55670-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [275 Votes, Top 5% Score]
